l</code>: metadata of the passed directive or component</p>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/global\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/global\n - api/core/global/ComponentDebugMetadata\n - api/core/global/DirectiveDebugMetadata\n - api/core/global/ngGetDirectiveMetadata#nggetdirectivemetadata\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L338-L381\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts#L338-L381\n-->"}